    "The Application 1 assumes user has provided a complete problem description.",
    "In many scenarios, users may not provide such a description at once, especially if they would like to gradually build up a complex problem.",
    "In light of this, it is necessary to guide them step by step through interactions to provide the necessary information for modelling optimization problems.",
    "We hope to start with the simplest chat, detect the missing information, and gradually guide users through interaction to provide necessary information indicating the variables, objective and constraints.",
    "Figure 3 shows an example where a coffee shop owner uses the system without any knowledge of optimization."
